          <title>
            <string language="en">Connecting cells in series</string>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Anschließende Zellen in den Serien</string>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cellules se reliantes en série</string>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Pilhas conectando em série</string>

            <string language="x-mt-el">Συνδέοντας κύτταρα στη σειρά</string>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Células que conectan en series</string>
          </title>
          <description>
            <string language="en">This illustration shows that connecting cells in series will add each cell's voltage to produce a higher voltage.</string>
          </description>
          <language>x-none</language>

            <string language="en">Cells</string>
          </keyword>

            <string language="en">series connection</string>
          </keyword>

          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-de">Diese Abbildung stellt dar, daß dem das 
Anschließen Zellen in den Serien Spannung jeder Zelle hinzufügt, um 
eine höhere Spannung zu produzieren.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-fr">Cette illustration montre que cela les cellules 
se relier en série ajoutera la tension de chaque cellules pour 
produire une tension plus élevée.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-pt">Esta ilustração mostra que isso pilhas conectar
em série adicionará a tensão de cada pilha para produzir uma 
tensão mais alta.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-it">Questa illustrazione mostra che quello cellule 
collegare in serie aggiungerà la tensione di ogni cellule per 
produrre un'più alta tensione.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-el">Αυτή η απεικόνιση δείχνει ότι τα συνδέοντας κύτταρα 
στη σειρά θα προσθέσουν την τάση κάθε κυττάρου για να παραγάγουν
μια υψηλότερη τάση.</string>
          </description>
          <description>
            <string language="x-mt-es">Esta ilustración muestra que eso las células el 
conectar en series agregará el voltaje de cada célula para producir 
un voltaje más alto.</string>
          </description>
